snippet: Brad Keselowski had just enough fuel left to take the checkered flag at Dover International Speedway in Delaware for his second victory in three weeks.
abstract: Brad Keselowski wins the AAA 400 auto race at Dover International Speedway in Delaware to take the Sprint Cup points lead.
lead_paragraph: Brad Keselowski had just enough fuel left to take the checkered flag at Dover International Speedway in Delaware for his second victory in three weeks.
